    title="Ray Arayilakath - Software Engineer"
    description="3+ years of experience growing engineering at YC-backed startups ðŸª´. researching tech justice at purdue university. building ethical and equitable software for the next 10 billion developers."
>
    <div
        class="flex flex-col items-start justify-start h-full w-full overflow-y-clip"
    >
        <div
